ore":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T13:31:42.000Z","msg":"仲有，文匯大公係咁煲佢係港獨，好似想同佢拉勇武港獨選民的票。<br />\n<br />\n跟本現任勝算大好多，又唔見黨報係咁抹黑現任？<br />\n<br />\n外黃內紅，明獨暗共。"},{"pid":"1828e3075b923ae855fcb4458bb07a9c01bfe89f","tid":1661862,"uid":266780,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-20T14:46:56.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://webb-site.com/dbpub/SFClicensees.asp?a=0&amp;p=131768\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwebb-site.com%2Fdbpub%2FSFClicensees.asp%3Fa%3D0%26p%3D131768&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=d68c9279\" target=\"_blank\">https://webb-site.com/dbpub/SFClicensees.asp?a=0&amp;p=131768</a><br />\n曾任以下中資出巿代表<br />\n交銀國際<br />\n博時基金 (中資)<a href=\"http://www.bosera.com.hk/zh/column/index.jsp?classid=0001000200020002\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bosera.com.hk%2Fzh%2Fcolumn%2Findex.jsp%3Fclassid%3D0001000200020002&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=3c64c884\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bosera.com.hk/zh/column/index.jsp?classid=0001000200020002</a><br />\n招銀國際<br />\n德健資產(擬似空殼公司)<br />\n西證國際(2014年被上海西南證券收購)<a href=\"https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%A5%BF%E8%AD%89%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%BD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fzh.m.wikipedia.org%2Fzh-hk%2F%25E8%25A5%25BF%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%259C%258B%25E9%259A%259B%25E8%25AD%2589%25E5%2588%25B8%25E8%2582%25A1%25E4%25BB%25BD&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=5bc0e948\" target=\"_blank\">https://zh.m.wikipedia.org/zh-hk/%E8%A5%BF%E8%AD%89%E5%9C%8B%E9%9A%9B%E8%AD%89%E5%88%B8%E8%82%A1%E4%BB%BD</a>"},{"pid":"4dfcf9aaa8d8bc3e96be4e458b53f478c78e5c3f","tid":1661862,"uid":235257,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:27:14.000Z","msg":"「蔡生，你𠝹票呀？」🤔<br />\n(民主選舉裡的「𠝹票」⋯)<br />\n<br />\n【聲明】<br />\n大家好。有報導說我在交銀國際工作，疑似中資機構資助出選區議會，志在「𠝹票」。<br />\n<br />\n首先，作為參與一個公平的選舉，我不認同用「𠝹票」這字眼，惡意套在一些候選人身上。這是侮辱公平的選舉，並且抺黑候選人，媒體指某些人「𠝹票」，有選舉舞弊之嫌。<br />\n<br />\n本人已在2018年2月辭任交銀國際，證監會亦有紀錄在案。某報章以本人工作背景做文章，其抹黑手法，實在可恥。明智的選民如對我本土立場有懷疑，可以參考本人對選管會的質詢信，也夠膽解釋什麼是「驅逐共黨，光復香港」、「天滅中共，全黨死清光」、 「香港自治」等口號。 特此聲明。<br />\n<br />\n#蔡佳鏗 #烏溪沙 #獨立候選人<br />\n#捍衛香港自治 #保護本土民生<br />\n#香港自治 #憲政民主<br />\n<br />\n- - - - -<br />\n<br />\n選舉廣告｜自行製作｜數量: 1｜2019年10月29日<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/106261684134905/posts/115140749913665/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F106261684134905%2Fposts%2F115140749913665%2F&d=JQdTOMZ4NvWA5L1F4kLiz3%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=cbc47dee\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/106261684134905/posts/115140749913665/</a>"},{"pid":"dbd376c93b953751515d04a83c06ded4d6cc8707","tid":1661862,"uid":316048,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-23T12:27:32.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">投票注意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所有人同我著紅橙黃綠青藍紫白衫<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n如果有人問你投比咩人/黨派，一定一定要答「建制派」，仲要加多句「反對暴力，希望香港回復和平」<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/mock.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n乜口號都唔好叫，買包花生番屋企坐定定<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/cook.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></strong>"}]}